In this travel pt1, I want to share some of my favorite places that I have traveled before the pandemic and places I have traveled this summer. Atlanta, GA (ATL) I have to admit I had a great time at Atlanta with friends. There is a lot to the city, a lot of places to visit such as Atlanta Botanical Garden, World of Coca-Cola, Georgia Aquarium and so on.
